            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add your<strong> bulgur wheat</strong> and your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> to the pan with 200ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [300ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [400ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Cook, covered, for 7-9 min or until almost all the water has absorbed</p><p>Once done, remove the pan from the heat and fluff with a fork – this is your <strong>Turkish-style kisir bulgur</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1711454210811-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
