          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1711454214730-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve your <strong>Turkish-style kisir bulgur </strong>with your <strong>roasted vegetables</strong> on top</p><p>Garnish with the<strong> toasted walnuts</strong>, <strong>chopped parsley </strong>and<strong> chopped mint</strong></p><p>Drizzle over the <strong>paprika mayo</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
